{
  "texts": [
    "A worrying issue is also related to using ChatGPT as a reference tool for students during exams.",
    "How can teachers ensure that students utilize it as a \"tutor\" rather than simply copying the entire answer provided by ChatGPT?",
    "This appears to be a difficult issue to address.",
    "Furthermore, teachers must help their students understand that generative AI, such as ChatGPT, can generate stereotypical responses based on the training data they receive.",
    "For instance, if it is trained on a dataset with biased or racist content, its generated responses may reflect those biases unless mitigated by careful training practices."
  ]
}